{"tid":2143061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TikTok稱全球業務至少值500億 否認微軟估值100億收購所有業務","createTime":"2020-08-07T01:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T01:35:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b48305f8e2356c6c53d7a7ee50f972a26e190314","tid":2143061,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:01:28.000Z","msg":"報道指微軟欲收購TikTok全球業務 字節跳動稱不屬實<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-08-07 00:27<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》引述知情人士報道，美國微軟公司正尋求收購抖音海外版TikTok的全球業務，除之前提及的北美、澳洲和新西蘭業務，還希望包括TIkTok在印度和歐洲的業務，而TikTok母公司字節跳動認為TikTok全球業務的價值超過500億美元。但字節跳動回應指，消息不屬實。路透社引述熟知談判詳情的消息人士則向指出，微軟未有提出收購TikTok所有業務。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，美國參議院一致通過法案，禁止聯邦僱員在政府提供的電子設備使用TikTok。美國眾議院上月亦通過類似法案，預料有關禁令或會成為法律。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2351035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2351035&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=9b331cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2351035</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【TikTok救亡】微軟擬2325億元收購TikTok 日本多地政府停用<br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n【新增內容】《CNBC》報道，微軟和TikTok計劃在9月15日限期之前的三周內完成收購談判。這筆交易的估值可能高達300億美元（約2,325億港元），或低至100億美元。如果交易達成，微軟已同意一年內將TikTok所有代碼從中國轉移到美國。<br />\n<br />\n據Wedbush Securities分析師Daniel Ives估算，TikTok美國業務約佔字節跳動總體估值40%，即400億美元左右，即收購價上限仍要比其估值低25%。<br />\n<br />\n微軟在周日證實，已與TikTok母公司字節跳動進行談判，以收購其在美國、加拿大、澳洲及新西蘭的業務，目前是唯一領先競標者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200806/DKU3CWX5SRCIHIM5XT6CKET2A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200806%2FDKU3CWX5SRCIHIM5XT6CKET2A4%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=50a2e19f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200806%2FDKU3CWX5SRCIHIM5XT6CKET2A4%2F&h=af8b0c36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200806/DKU3CWX5SRCIHIM5XT6CKET2A4/</a>"},{"pid":"919376021bb3f989a01d3940e9709fe016ccdd1b","tid":2143061,"uid":166733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己值10000億"},{"pid":"94d01baf0275908f80d4193287f6c8ea24c50752","tid":2143061,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"500萬係咁多"},{"pid":"dff1e4d682beb6993fb15b66b724fb7c91e84a44","tid":2143061,"uid":120859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:06:30.000Z","msg":"其實Twitter 收購vine 之後又殺咗佢係做mud鳩"},{"pid":"7883e6ecb2436f80407778b0c663f1ee892351d0","tid":2143061,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:08:41.000Z","msg":"最多咪50億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f47a51cfa46149341ba35e95a7a2832b971bc1a","tid":2143061,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:11:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">支那已經係香港成日做低D 企業O既股價, 然後低價收購</span>"},{"pid":"c512947e67f0110a6ce3b1413e92a175ea314b9b","tid":2143061,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"談判新策略<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:500億<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:100億<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:500億<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:50億<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:500億<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:5億<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:50億 ok?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:不了"},{"pid":"0626b1575cff35d707fca73144bbd26cc37aebf6","tid":2143061,"uid":89869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T01:18:20.000Z","msg":"侵：呢間野就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h